    <item>
      <title>特朗普呼吁废除联邦紧急事务管理局，扩大与联邦政府的斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-calls-for-abolishing-fema-expanding-battle-against-feds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示应该取消联邦紧急事务管理局，此举将扩大他对联邦官僚机构的斗争，他曾谴责联邦官僚机构是损害其利益的“深层政府”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-calls-for-abolishing-fema-expanding-battle-against-feds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 16:32:33 GMT</pubDate>
